# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  1. GET MY MATCHES
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### ✅ All matches — perfect first, then partial
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ✅ Filter — perfect matches only
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?type=perfect
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ✅ Filter — partial matches only
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?type=partial
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ✅ Filter — by skill category
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?category=tech
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ✅ Filter — by skill level
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?level=beginner
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ✅ Sort — by rating (default is score)
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?sort=rating
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ✅ Sort — by number of sessions completed
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?sort=sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ✅ Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ✅ Combined filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?type=perfect&category=tech&sort=rating&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ❌ No token (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches

### ❌ Invalid type value (400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?type=superMatch
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ❌ Invalid sort value (400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?sort=alphabetical
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  2. GET SINGLE MATCH
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### ✅ Get match detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches/{{matchId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ❌ Match not found (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ❌ Invalid UUID (400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches/not-a-uuid
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ❌ Match belongs to someone else (403)
###   Use a matchId from another user's matches
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches/e492ee4c-99a6-462a-9d43-241d431cb669
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  3. MANUAL RECALCULATE (admin only)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### ✅ Admin — trigger recalculation
POST {{baseUrl}}/matches/recalculate
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ❌ Regular user — forbidden (403)
POST {{baseUrl}}/matches/recalculate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ❌ No token (401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/matches/recalculate
